Summary: Starlike Moving in a flight pattern
divs: Sighting Details Walked out side to the patio at Willow plaza, on the White MT. HWY. One other individual and I noticed a glowing(Bright white) starlike orb moving NE from the W. The orb dimmed out and then dimmed or traveled away. We both initially thought the flight path of this starlike orb was unusual as it did not have any FAA regulated strobes as most aircraft is required by law.
